metadata.name: The Explorer
metadata.description:
You must assemble your party for the pixel dungeon. All roads start from The Explorer. Skilled in lockpicking and treasure seeking, The Explorer doesn't lend much to combat but can really make the difference when it comes to pulling treasure from the dungeon. Explorers can upgraded to other classes through burning.
